    For each classifier from one ensemble and each possible class: confidence of the classifier that the instance belongs to the class.
    Label
    Aggregates the votes from multiple ensembles that the instance belongs to one particular label.
    Votes
    Represents the votes of multiple ensembles for one particular instance: the list of all possible labels and their assigned measures (see Label) the total number of ensembles that voted for this instance.
